General.Name: Panoramic Resources Ltd
General.Description: Panoramic Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration, evaluation, development of mineral tenements and projects. It explores for nickel, cobalt, and copper deposits. The company holds 100% interests in the Savannah nickel project located in the East Kimberly, Western Australia. Panoramic Resources Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
